  "detailed_description": "PARTHIAN STRIKE is a TPS robot piloting game.<br>It is designed to give players a sense of accomplishment in defeating powerful enemies while gaining a real feel for piloting a machine.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2057040/extras/61b2daff2d93915428c55901db03c569.avif?t=1705063828\" width=532 height=299 /></span><br><br>The goal of the game is to pilot a robot to attack and destroy enemy robots.<br>There are several types of missions besides defeating the enemy, such as stage traversal and defense, but the game is basically designed in a way that allows the player to focus on piloting and fighting in 1vs1 situations.<br><br>Bug and bug report board<br>",
  "about_the_game": "PARTHIAN STRIKE is a TPS robot piloting game.<br>It is designed to give players a sense of accomplishment in defeating powerful enemies while gaining a real feel for piloting a machine.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2057040/extras/61b2daff2d93915428c55901db03c569.avif?t=1705063828\" width=532 height=299 /></span><br><br>The goal of the game is to pilot a robot to attack and destroy enemy robots.<br>There are several types of missions besides defeating the enemy, such as stage traversal and defense, but the game is basically designed in a way that allows the player to focus on piloting and fighting in 1vs1 situations.<br><br>Bug and bug report board<br>",
